HEADWORD: Nepaulese
<hw>Nep`au*lese"</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <def>Of
or pertaining to Nepal (formerly written Nepaul), a kingdom North of
India; same as <altname>Nepalese</altname>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n. sing.
& pl.</pos> <def>A native or natives of Nepal.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

